dc_title_s: Geologic map of the Elkhorn Hills quadrangle, San Luis Obispo and Kern Counties, California
dc_description_s: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Contour interval 50 feet." "Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle ELKHORN HILLS, CA 1954, DMA 2054 II SE -- Series V895." "First printing, August 2005." Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology. Includes "pertinent references."
dc_publisher_s: Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History
